template.description:
Annotation template, checking documents pulled from ES/OS have already been annotated via a sqlite DB.
Will call a medcat service to annotate documents then return and update the sqlite db with document ID so it will not be sent for annotations again.
Finally will add annotations to ES/OS indexes.
template.name: SQL_Annotate_Per_Doc
